<H3> <TI>   Djindjic Elected President </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3001095594 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 0010 GMT 30 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3001095594 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Belgrade, 29 Jan (TANJUG) -- Zoran Djindjic, 
hitherto chairman of the Democratic Party's [DS] executive 
committee is the party's new president beginning this evening. 
The extraordinary assembly of the DS, which has been in session 
since this morning [29 January], elected Djindjic as the party's 
new president this evening. The session was attended by 357 
delegates and 286 voted in favor of Djindjic. [passage omitted] 

