<F P=100> POLAND </F>
<H3> <TI>   Deputy Finance Minister Dismissed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2801164694 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1215 GMT 28 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2801164694 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, 28 Jan--The government press office has 
announced that the chairman of the Council of Ministers today 
dismissed Stefan Kawalec, under secretary of state in the 
Ministry of Finance, from his post. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

