<H3> <TI>   Fishing Under Secretary Resigns To Enter Politics </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY0101214494 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 
1421 GMT 31 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> PY0101214494 </F>
<F P=104>  Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Mar del Plata, 31 Dec (NA) -- Under Secretary of 
Fishing Fernando Gutierrez submitted his resignation on 29 
December to Agriculture, Livestock and Fishing Secretary Felipe 
Sola, reported reliable sources of that secretariat. 
  Gutierrez apparently conveyed to Secretary Sola his decision 
to leave his post in order to get involved in political 
activities for the Justicialist Party. [passage omitted] 
  The sources indicated that Gutierrez' replacement "is not 
yet 
known," and that the new appointment will not be made until 
February, after Sola returns from the vacation he is taking in 
this city. 

</TEXT>

